channel.title: Highly edited delta v2 [Delta cleaned]
channel.description:
[CENTER]This may or not be the last version, I'm not sure. I've spent hours up hours on this, and finally got it to the point that I believe it is good enough to be released. In v2, I got the client class size down to [B]180KBS[/B]. There is a handler for anything and everything, deathstages, trading, loading, etc. Everything has been cleaned and packaged. Also, I am naming it RS2007, because I packed the 459 sideicons into the cache.
[B][SIZE=3]Features:[/SIZE][/B] Dialogue handler Handlers Better packaging No uppercase folders Cleaned out client class Client 180KBS No dead code 459 sideicons Faster combat Much more.
To any and all delta users, use this if you want to get somewhere. It can still be LARGELY improved, but if you know what you're doing this could become something great.
Picture: [IMG]http://i779.photobucket.com/albums/yy71/lostmyphat/clean.png[/img]
Combat: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PTz23p6cD2E
Source and client packed in: [url=http://up.ht/xYTpU2]http://up.ht/xYTpU2[/url] [/CENTER]
